{"words":[{"word":"medicinal","count":7},{"word":"soup","count":6},{"word":"spoon","count":5},{"word":"oh","count":3},{"word":"chixia","count":3},{"word":"medicine","count":3},{"word":"any","count":3},{"word":"pharmacy","count":3},{"word":"water","count":3},{"word":"monkvyrid","count":3},{"word":"recipe","count":3},{"word":"help","count":2},{"word":"ms","count":2},{"word":"someone","count":2},{"word":"injuries","count":2},{"word":"away","count":2},{"word":"essence","count":2},{"word":"medley","count":2},{"word":"knew","count":2},{"word":"cuisine","count":2},{"word":"always","count":2},{"word":"new","count":2},{"word":"pre-made","count":2},{"word":"everyone","count":2},{"word":"potions","count":2},{"word":"big","count":2},{"word":"pyrite","count":2},{"word":"uncle","count":2},{"word":"wei","count":2},{"word":"last","count":2},{"word":"hello","count":1},{"word":"brought","count":1},{"word":"picking","count":1},{"word":"else","count":1},{"word":"feeling","count":1},{"word":"weather","count":1},{"word":"seen","count":1},{"word":"doctor","count":1},{"word":"prescriptions","count":1},{"word":"habit","count":1},{"word":"picked","count":1},{"word":"running","count":1},{"word":"sometimes","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"struggle","count":1},{"word":"describe","count":1},{"word":"symptoms","count":1},{"word":"ask","count":1},{"word":"lot","count":1},{"word":"questions","count":1},{"word":"clearer","count":1},{"word":"picture","count":1},{"word":"obviously","count":1},{"word":"male","count":1},{"word":"gentleman","count":1},{"word":"female","count":1},{"word":"lady","count":1},{"word":"said","count":1},{"word":"carried","count":1},{"word":"forget","count":1},{"word":"safety","count":1},{"word":"reigning","count":1},{"word":"champ","count":1},{"word":"medication","count":1},{"word":"leaderboard","count":1},{"word":"wholeheartedly","count":1},{"word":"appreciate","count":1},{"word":"support","count":1},{"word":"topping","count":1},{"word":"charts","count":1},{"word":"result","count":1},{"word":"discounts","count":1},{"word":"felt","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"grandmother","count":1},{"word":"generation","count":1},{"word":"caltrops","count":1},{"word":"kudzu","count":1},{"word":"honeysuckles","count":1},{"word":"handful","count":1},{"word":"gemberries","count":1},{"word":"pulled","count":1},{"word":"poultry","count":1},{"word":"breast","count":1},{"word":"simmer","count":1},{"word":"boiled","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"stir","count":1},{"word":"golden-handled","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"coriolus","count":1},{"word":"perilla","count":1},{"word":"lemongrass","count":1},{"word":"serve","count":1},{"word":"base","count":1},{"word":"leans","count":1},{"word":"towards","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"ingredients","count":1},{"word":"dilute","count":1},{"word":"effect","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"learn","count":1},{"word":"dietary","count":1},{"word":"therapy","count":1},{"word":"trouble","count":1},{"word":"remember","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"often","count":1},{"word":"tastes","count":1},{"word":"bitter","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"thinking","count":1},{"word":"ways","count":1},{"word":"palatable","count":1},{"word":"making","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"preserve","count":1},{"word":"healing","count":1},{"word":"qualities","count":1},{"word":"getting","count":1},{"word":"rid","count":1},{"word":"bitterness","count":1},{"word":"enjoyable","count":1},{"word":"seems","count":1},{"word":"ancient","count":1},{"word":"old","count":1},{"word":"term","count":1},{"word":"pharmacies","count":1},{"word":"referring","count":1},{"word":"hold","count":1},{"word":"stuff","count":1},{"word":"recovery","count":1},{"word":"synthesis","count":1},{"word":"consider","count":1},{"word":"bonus","count":1},{"word":"treat","count":1},{"word":"stay","count":1},{"word":"safe","count":1},{"word":"alright","count":1},{"word":"keep","count":1},{"word":"guard","count":1},{"word":"exploring","count":1},{"word":"barging","count":1},{"word":"scaring","count":1},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"heading","count":1},{"word":"auntie","count":1},{"word":"panhua","count":1},{"word":"count","count":1},{"word":"learning","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"golden","count":1},{"word":"handle","count":1},{"word":"shop","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"haha","count":1},{"word":"worries","count":1},{"word":"spotted","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"dropped","count":1},{"word":"asked","count":1},{"word":"curiosity","count":1},{"word":"best","count":1},{"word":"weapon","count":1},{"word":"maker","count":1},{"word":"jinzhou","count":1},{"word":"tucked","count":1},{"word":"counting","count":1},{"word":"solve","count":1},{"word":"mystery","count":1},{"word":"along","count":1},{"word":"step","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Hello there, how can I help...? Oh, Ms. Chixia?","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"What brought you here? Picking up medicine for someone else, or feeling under the weather? Any injuries? Have you seen a doctor? Need any prescriptions?","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Oh no, it’s just a habit I’ve picked up from running this pharmacy. Sometimes people struggle to describe their symptoms, so I ask a lot of questions to get a clearer picture.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Obviously, just like this {Male=gentleman;Female=lady} said, once you get carried away, you forget your own safety!","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Ms. Chixia, you’re the reigning champ on our pharmacy’s medication leaderboard. While I wholeheartedly appreciate your support, topping the charts won’t result in any discounts here.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Essence Medley Soup? I felt like I heard it from my grandmother or someone of her generation.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Let's see... Caltrops, Kudzu, Honeysuckles, a handful of Gemberries, and some pulled poultry breast. Simmer with water from the Monkvyrid. Once it's boiled, give it a stir with a golden-handled spoon... Water from the Monkvyrid? Isn't that the medicinal soup made from Coriolus, Perilla, and Lemongrass?","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Who knew the medicinal soup could serve as a base... In a way, it leans towards medicinal cuisine. But with so many ingredients, wouldn’t it dilute the medicinal effect? There’s always something new to learn in dietary therapy.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"No need to go through all that trouble. Remember where you are? A pharmacy! I’ve got some pre-made medicinal soup right here.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Good medicine often tastes bitter, so I've been thinking of ways to make it more palatable.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"By making it into medicinal cuisine, we preserve its healing qualities while getting rid of the bitterness, so it’s enjoyable for everyone.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"This recipe seems ancient. The Monkvyrid water is an old term from pharmacies, referring to that medicinal soup. Hold on, I’ve got the pre-made stuff for you.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Oh, and here are some new recovery and synthesis potions. Consider them a bonus.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"But even with potions to treat your injuries, stay safe out there, alright? Always keep your guard up when exploring.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Don’t be like Chixia, just barging in and scaring everyone.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"So, are you two heading back to help Auntie Panhua with this Essence Medley Soup? If so, count me in on learning that recipe too!","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Wait, isn’t the golden handle spoon that big pyrite spoon from Uncle Wei’s shop? I thought you both knew.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Haha, no worries. I spotted that spoon the last time I dropped off medicine at Uncle Wei’s and asked out of curiosity.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011},{"text":"Why does the best weapon maker in Jinzhou have a big pyrite spoon tucked away? Well, I’m counting on you to solve that mystery, along with the last step of the recipe.","quest_name":"A Taste of Everything","quest_id":880000011}]}